A customer buys a DL380 asking for three years coverage and 13×5 support availability.
Which HP service solution should you offer?
A. Flexible HP Care Pack
B. Fixed HP Care Pack
C. HP Break-fix Service Contract
D. HP Service Contract
Answer: B
Which service offers a customer the ability to manage their IT operational costs and system
performance?
A. HP Hardware and Software Break-fix
B. HP Implementation and Commissioning
C. HP Installation and Site Assessment
D. HP Care Pack and Account Management
Answer: C
What identifies a customer as needing an HP Support Contract at the point of sale?
A. contract value less than $10k
B. common service levels
C. requirement of more than three service levels
D. common expiry date
Answer: C
